you forgot {{champion:102}} 

On a smaller scale we also have {{champion:77}} (phoenix stance) and some champs who use explosives.

But anyway I think more fire champs are ok,but they shouldn't be exclusively themed on fire,because thats kinda {{champion:63}} s thing(annie is mainly identified by being a creepy child).The ice champs from the freljord are actually a good example of how to do this,as almost  none are exclusively based on having ice powers{{champion:22}} is a ranger,{{champion:34}} a phoenix,{{champion:201}} a shieldguard/strongman,{{champion:20}} a yeti rider,{{champion:113}} a warmonger/savage rider.I guess {{champion:127}} could kinda count as she is an ice-witch,similar to an ice queen.
